:'''Tanya:''' Same as before. But... have you heard? The Underworld and Overworld are being connected soon! I knew the Supreme Guardian would never abandon us, and withdrawing Guards was just out of circumstances... Great! We have hope!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Do you think it's the work of the Supreme Guardian?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501024185-->
::'''Tanya:''' Of course, it is! The Supreme Guardian is far-sighted, and more powerful than us commoners in every way. It's a pity then that some villagers have taken to slandering the name of the Supreme Guardian...
::'''Tanya:''' Especially that Wildfire and the vagrants, endlessly complaining about how the Supreme Guardian abandoned the Underworld... Now she's back. Hmph, I'll have to see how they spin this one.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} You seem excited.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501024187-->
::'''Tanya:''' What do you mean? Don't you feel excited, too?
::'''Tanya:''' Once the Silvermane Guards return to the Underworld, the glorious future of this place will be obvious to all.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501024189-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501024189-->
:'''Tanya:''' Hey... Why haven't the Silvermane Guards come down yet? It only feels safe to have them patrol around the town!
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:'''Tanya:''' My husband has been coming back early these days, and peace and quiet has been in short supply. Let's add another dish.
:'''Tanya:''' But... I'll have to buy everything and cook it myself... Ack, I really miss those days when we could date up there... I wonder what that man from the Guards is up to these days...
:'''Tanya:''' Ah? It's you. You startled me. I thought it was some dense vagrants.
:'''Tanya:''' What do you want from me?
:<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_500010702-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500010702-->
:'''Tanya:''' I'm telling you, don't you dare be like those vagrants and dream that you're smarter than Madam Cocolia and the government.
:'''Tanya:''' The Supreme Guardian will never abandon us. And the Silvermane Guards have to return some time. Just you wait and see!
:<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
