::'''Tanya:''' Ack, these Wildfire guys... and the vagrants, they're so annoying... can't you just chill out?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_5010276_10-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_5010276_10-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You don't like Wildfire?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027605-->
:::'''Tanya:''' I don't hate Wildfire. I just think they're too idealistic. I might be just a housewife, but I know a thing or two about the outside world.
:::'''Tanya:''' Food, water, waste disposal, logistics &mdash; it's a mess from head to toe in the Underworld. Without these basics guaranteed, how do you plan on defending your home? Why, it's just a daydream!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You seem to hate the vagrants.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027608-->
:::'''Tanya:''' Of course. They stir up trouble all day. They should settle down and get stable jobs.
:::'''Tanya:''' I know some people lost their homes because of the monsters, but is it that hard for able-bodied people to find jobs? You can't let your situation dictate your predicament, instead you have to adapt. Do you get me?
:::'''Tanya:''' So that's how I taught my kids &mdash; "If you don't listen to your parents, you'll end up as a vagrant when you grow up!"
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501027609-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027609-->
::'''Tanya:''' Why are you asking so many questions? You don't look like a vagrant. Are you part of the Wildfire? No, you don't dress like you're from the Underworld... Are you from the Overworld?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_5010276_21-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_5010276_21-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You misunderstand.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm just passing through.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027615-->
